From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: SerenityOS Developers <serenityos@serenityos.org>
Date: Thu, 1 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add SerenityOS errno location

Add SerenityOS to the __errno_location link_name group. SerenityOS uses
__errno_location (same as Linux/DragonFly/Emscripten).

---
 src/unix.rs | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/src/unix.rs b/src/unix.rs
index 5536eef..41d262a 100644
--- a/src/unix.rs
+++ b/src/unix.rs
@@ -95,6 +95,7 @@ extern "C" {
             target_os = "redox",
             target_os = "dragonfly",
             target_os = "emscripten",
+            target_os = "serenity",
         ),
         link_name = "__errno_location"
     )]
